    public class C_RasterGraph
extends C_Raster
implements I_transportation_constants
    Classe encapsulant les informations sur le graphe Dans cette classe nous allons constuire principalement le graphe et sa matrice d'adjacence (edgesList) en utiliasant les classes C_Graph et C_SoilCellGraphed
    Author:
    Mboup 05/08/2012
    See Also:
    C_Graph, C_SoilCellGraphed

      • buildGraphsFromLandPlots

        public void buildGraphsFromLandPlots(java.util.TreeSet<C_LandPlot> aLandPlotList,
                            java.lang.String... graphTypeParam)
        This method build new graphs and update the olds for a group of landPlot in the same groundType.
        This method can also build a graph (or a portion of graph) contained in another landPlot with optional parameter;
        e.g., build a graph corresponding to the portion of road located on the Groundnut Basin.
        Parameters:
        aLandPlotList -
        graphTypeParam - optional

      • identifyTypeLandPlots

        public java.util.TreeSet<C_LandPlot> identifyTypeLandPlots(java.lang.String groundType)
        This method scan all the soilCellMatrix and detect all landPlots with the groundType in param;
        taking into account that a soilCell may belong simultaneously to several landPlots with differents groundTypes.
        This method doesn't update old landPlots but it build new ones.
        Parameters:
        groundType -
        Returns:
        a list of landPlot author: P.A. Mboup, 2014, rev. JLF 11.2014
